{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e9b6f8f8-9c84-4dd2-89f1-6e3bb1b4f0f1",
    "name": "Pro-Enroll API (Bearer Token)",
    "description": "Pro-Enroll + Pro-Fix Customer API with **JWT Bearer token** auth.\n\n## Import\n1. `Pro-Enroll-API.postman_collection.json` (this file)\n2. `Pro-Enroll-API-Live.postman_environment.json` (or Local)\n3. Select environment: **Pro-Enroll Live**\n\n## Get a token\n1. **01 Get Token → Send OTP** — saves `request_id` + `otp` (when `debug_otp` in response)\n2. **01 Get Token → Verify OTP** — saves `access_token` + `refresh_token`\n3. All **🔒 Bearer** folders use `Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}` automatically\n\n## base_url\n`http://98.93.105.128/pro_enroll_api`\n\nDocs: `docs/POSTMAN_LIVE_FULL_REFERENCE.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (!pm.request.headers.has('Accept')) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'Accept', value: 'application/json' });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 Flow — Login & Test",
      "description": "Run in order with Collection Runner. Step 1–2 get token; step 3–5 use Bearer automatically.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Send OTP",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "try {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.test('success', () => pm.expect(json.success).to.eql(true));",
                  "  const d = json.data || {};",
                  "  if (d.request_id) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('request_id', d.request_id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('request_id', d.request_id);",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (d.debug_otp) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('otp', d.debug_otp);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('otp', d.debug_otp);",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone_e164\": \"{{phone_e164}}\",\n  \"mode\": \"sign_up\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/otp/send"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Verify OTP",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "try {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.test('success', () => pm.expect(json.success).to.eql(true));",
                  "  const d = json.data || {};",
                  "  if (d.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('access_token', d.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', d.access_token);",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (d.refresh_token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('refresh_token', d.refresh_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', d.refresh_token);",
                  "  }",
                  "} catch (e) {}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"request_id\": \"{{request_id}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\",\n  \"mode\": \"sign_up\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/otp/verify"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Validate Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('token valid', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().success).to.eql(true));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/validate"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/v1/auth/me"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Splash",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{base_url}}/v1/screens/splash"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
